<ab><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hall<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>Jac<ex>ob</ex></expan>
<expan>Grol<ex>and</ex></expan> und <expan>Sebolt<ex>en</ex></expan>
